<doc id="229505" wikidata="Q7608088" url="?curid=229505" title="Stepchild (disambiguation)">
<text>A stepchild is the daughter or son of one&#x27;s spouse but not of oneself

Stepchild may also refer to:
* &quot;Stepchild&quot; (film), a 1947 American drama film
* &quot;Stepchild&quot;, a song written by Bob Dylan as &quot;Am I Your Stepchild?&quot; (1978), sung by Solomon Burke on his 2002 album &quot;Don&#x27;t Give Up on Me&quot; and by Jerry Lee Lewis on &quot;Rock &amp; Roll Time&quot; 2014
* &quot;Stepchild&quot;, a single by Billie Jo Spears from her 1969 album &quot;Miss Sincerity&quot;, see Billie Jo Spears discography</text><links>
